<a name="fiery_avenger"></a>
<font color="#FFFFFF" face="Arial">
<strong>Fiery Avenger</strong>
<font size=-1></font><BR>
Skill: <a href="/weapons/2h_slash.shtml">2H Slash</a><BR>
Damage per second - 15.23<BR>
Damage 33 - Delay 44<BR>
Weight: 0.1 - All Races<BR>
Classes: <a href="/paladin/weapons/2h_slash.shtml">PAL</a><BR>
Effect: <a href="http://www.maximumeq.com/spells/individual/flame_shock.shtml?spellID=165">Flame Shock</a><BR>
<font color=red>
(Magic) (No Drop) (Lore) <BR>
(STR +15) (WIS +15) (CHA +10) (Sv Magic +5) (Sv Cold +5) (Sv Poison +5) (HP +25) (Mana +25) </font>
<BR>
Obtained through a long quest, ending in the Plane of Sky.<BR>
Submitted By: Pipping<BR>

